title: Watley's last-minute run carries Raiders past Ridgeview
text:
Watley's last-minute run carries Raiders past Ridgeview 
Sat, Oct 3, 2015 @ 12:11 am 
ORANGE PARK 25 
RIDGEVIEW 20 
Senior RB Terrek Watley scored on a 28 yard run with 37 seconds left to rally the Raiders (4-2, 1-1) in a District 5-5A game... OP QB Tymious Goodman rushed for 176 yards on 20 carries and scored on runs of 28, 60 and 73 yards. ... Ridgeview (1-4, 1-2) was led by junior RB Kenny Zamor, who rambled for 148 yards on 22 attempts and scored on TD runs of five, 46 and 15 yards. Zamorâ€™s last score put the Panthers up 20-19 with 2:23 left in the game.
